{"url": "https://www.ics.uci.edu/~kobsa/courses/ICS104/course-notes/deficiencies.htm", "content": "<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN\">\n<html>\n  <head>\n    <title>Deficiencies in Human Information Processing</title>\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html;\n      charset=windows-1252\">\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <p><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\"><b><font\n            size=\"+6\">\"Deficiencies\" in Human Information Processing<br>\n          </font></b></font></p>\n    <p>&nbsp;</p>\n    <p><big><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\"><big><font\n              size=\"5\"><big>1. </big></font></big></font><font size=\"5\"><big><font\n              face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\">Limited attention</font></big></font><br>\n      </big></p>\n    <big>\n    </big>\n    <p><big><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><big>2.\n            Limited memory (both long-term and short-term</big></font><font\n          size=\"5\"><big><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\">)</font></big></font></big><br>\n    </p>\n    <p><big><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><big>3. </big></font></big><big><font\n          face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><big>Limited\n            cognitive resources (\"time-sharing\"), specifically under\n            time pressure<br>\n          </big></font></big></p>\n    <big>\n    </big><big>\n    </big>\n    <p><big><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><big>4.\n            Recognition is easy, recall is hard</big></font><br>\n      </big></p>\n    <big>\n    </big>\n    <p><big><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><big>5. </big></font></big><big><font\n          face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><big><big><font\n                face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><big>Recognition\n                  is selective and task-driven</big></font></big></big></font></big><big><font\n          face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><big><big><br>\n            </big><big>\n            </big></big></font></big></p>\n    <p><big><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><big>6. </big></font></big><big><font\n          face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><big><big><font\n                face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><big>Slow\n                  and inaccurate when processing text</big></font></big></big></font></big><br>\n    </p>\n    <p><big><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><big>7. </big></font></big><big><font\n          face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><big><big><font\n                face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><big>Vision\n                  is optimized to see structure</big></font></big></big></font></big><big><font\n          face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><big><big><br>\n            </big><big> </big></big></font></big>\n    </p>\n    <p>\n    </p>\n    <p><big><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><big>8. </big></font></big><big><font\n          face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><big><big><font\n                face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><big>Frequent\n                  errors</big></font></big></big></font></big><big><font\n          face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><big><big><br>\n            </big><big> </big></big></font></big>\n    </p>\n    <p><big><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><big>9. </big></font></big><big><font\n          face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><big><big><font\n                face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><big>Decisions\n                  are rarely rational, but based on \"shortcuts\" and\n                  prone to bias<br>\n                </big></font></big></big></font></big></p>\n    <p><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"5\"><big>Etc. etc.</big><br>\n      </font></p>\n    <p>&nbsp;</p>\n    <p align=\"right\">&nbsp; </p>\n  </body>\n</html>\n", "encoding": "ascii"}